#: src/dos/programs/loadrom.cpp:107
#, c-format, no-wrap
msgctxt "PROGRAM_LOADROM_HELP_LONG"
msgid ""
"Load a ROM image of the video BIOS or IBM BASIC.\n"
"\n"
"Usage:\n"
"  [color=light-green]loadrom [color=light-cyan]IMAGEFILE[reset]\n"
"\n"
"Parameters:\n"
"  [color=light-cyan]IMAGEFILE[reset]  video BIOS or IBM BASIC ROM image\n"
"\n"
"Notes:\n"
"  After loading an IBM BASIC ROM image into the emulated ROM with the command,\n"
"  you can run the original IBM BASIC interpreter program in DOSBox Staging.\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  [color=light-green]loadrom[reset] [color=light-cyan]bios.rom[reset]\n"
msgstr ""
"Charge une image ROM du BIOS vidéo ou d'IBM BASIC.\n"
"\n"
"Utilisation :\n"
" [color=light-green]loadrom [color=light-cyan]IMAGEFILE[reset]\n"
"\n"
"Paramètres :\n"
" [color=light-cyan]IMAGEFILE[reset]  image ROM du BIOS vidéo ou d'IBM BASIC\n"
"\n"
"Notes :\n"
" Après chargement d'une ROM IBM BASIC dans la ROM émulée via cette\n"
" commande, vous pouvez exécuter l'interpréteur IBM BASIC original dans\n"
" DOSBox Staging.\n"
"\n"
"Exemples :\n"
" [color=light-green]loadrom[reset] [color=light-cyan]bios.rom[reset]\n"

